<% content_for :title, "About LoanFlow Pro" %>

<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10">
      <div class="card shadow-lg border-0 rounded-3">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white text-center py-4 rounded-top-3">
          <h1 class="mb-0 fs-3">About UE Loans - Loan Management System</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body p-5">

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-primary mb-3 fs-4">System Overview</h2>
            <p class="lead text-secondary">
              **UE Loans ** is a robust and intuitive platform designed to streamline and optimize the entire loan management lifecycle. From initial application to final repayment, our system provides comprehensive tools for financial institutions, microfinance organizations, and loan officers to efficiently manage their portfolios.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted">
              **Purpose:** This platform empowers your team to meticulously track, analyze, and report on loan applications, disbursements, and repayments, ensuring transparency and operational excellence.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted">
              **Key functionalities include:**
            </p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>Efficient Loan Application Tracking & Processing</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>Real-time Loan Performance Analysis</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>Automated Repayment Scheduling & Delinquency Monitoring</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>Comprehensive Loan Portfolio Reporting</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>Secure User & Role Management</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-primary mb-3 fs-4">Who It's For</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">
              LoanFlow Pro is tailored for professionals within the lending sector seeking an advanced, reliable, and user-friendly system.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><i class="bi bi-person-fill text-info me-2"></i>**Loan Officers:** To manage individual client applications and monitor their loan statuses.</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-briefcase-fill text-info me-2"></i>**Financial Managers:** To gain holistic insights into the loan portfolio's health and performance.</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-people-fill text-info me-2"></i>**Administrative Staff:** To handle data entry, generate reports, and manage user accounts efficiently.</li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-shield-fill text-info me-2"></i>**Compliance Officers:** To ensure all loan processes adhere to regulatory standards.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-primary mb-3 fs-4">Key Features</h2>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                  <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow text-success me-3 fs-3"></i>
                  <div>
                    <h5 class="mb-1">Real-time Dashboard</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Instant overview of key metrics and recent activities.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                  <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-bar-graph-fill text-success me-3 fs-3"></i>
                  <div>
                    <h5 class="mb-1">Comprehensive Reports</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Generate detailed loan portfolio, repayment, and delinquency reports.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                  <i class="bi bi-bell-fill text-success me-3 fs-3"></i>
                  <div>
                    <h5 class="mb-1">Automated Reminders</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Notifications for upcoming payments and overdue accounts.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                  <i class="bi bi-activity text-success me-3 fs-3"></i>
                  <div>
                    <h5 class="mb-1">User Activity & Audit Trails</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Track all system interactions for accountability and compliance.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-primary mb-3 fs-4">Our Commitment</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">
              LoanFlow Pro was developed with a deep understanding of the challenges in microfinance and traditional lending. Our mission is to provide an intuitive, secure, and scalable solution that enhances operational efficiency and data accuracy, allowing your team to focus on serving your clients effectively.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-primary mb-3 fs-4">Version Information</h2>
            <p class="text-muted mb-1">
              **Current Version:** 1.0.0
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted small">
              *Last Updated: <%= Date.today.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>* (You can hardcode this or fetch it if you have a version tracking system)
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-primary mb-3 fs-4">Contact & Support</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">
              For any inquiries, technical support, or feedback regarding LoanFlow Pro, please reach out to our dedicated support team.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><i class="bi bi-envelope-fill text-danger me-2"></i> Email: <a href="mailto: " class="text-decoration-none">ueloans@support.com</a></li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-question-circle-fill text-warning me-2"></i> For user manuals and FAQs, please visit our <a href="ueloans.org" class="text-decoration-none">ueloans.org</a></li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-primary mb-3 fs-4">Disclaimer</h2>
            <p class="text-muted small mb-0">
              *Data presented within UE Loans is for internal operational use only and should be handled in accordance with your organization's data privacy and security policies.*
            </p>
          </section>

        </div>
        <div class="card-footer bg-light text-center py-3 rounded-bottom-3">
          <p class="text-muted small mb-0">&copy; <%= Time.now.year %> LoanFlow Pro. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>